--)Gems(avro)
#)install.remote
$ gem list --local avro
$ gem list --remote avro
$ gem install avro
Fetching: multi_json-1.10.1.gem (100%)
Fetching: avro-1.7.7.gem (100%)
Successfully installed multi_json-1.10.1
Successfully installed avro-1.7.7
2 gems installed

--)Run
First run the server as:

ruby -r 'rubygems' ./sample_ipc_server.rb

Then run the client as:

ruby -r 'rubygems' ./sample_ipc_client.rb avro_user pat Hello_World
